This is STATISTICS, NOT TRIBALISM 🙂🙂🙂.

-NICCO MOVERS SACCO BUS Conductor KILLED this student by throwing him out of moving Bus,on Thika Road 🤔🤔🤔.

-Deaths by THROWING passengers OUT of moving VEHICLES occur in Vehicles SERVING KIKUYUS ESTATES IN NAIROBI ( 99%)🙂

-WHY?

-Verify all these types of Deaths in Nairobi ROADS and their is a pattern;

-The vehicles that have been all involved in this Heinous act serve Githurai, Kasarani, Kahawa West, Thika ,Ngong, Ruiru....,The KIKUYUS ESTATES IN NAIROBI. 

-You will never Hear such cases in VEHICLES estates dominated by other Tribes in Nairobi like LUOS, LUHYAS, KAMBAS, SOMALIS.... 

-Why are VEHICLES serving KIKUYUS DOMINATED ESTATES in NAIROBI have culture of IMPUNITY,
RECKLESSNESS, & SELFISHNESS?

-The Kikuyus who saw this student being thrown out of Nicco buses because he lacked ksh.30 as fare, you people  ( 20+ passengers)could not give 30/= to the conductor to Save the life of this STUDENT?

-VERY SELFISH TRIBE, KIKUYUS 🙂🙂🙂🙂🙂.

-I urge @ntsa_kenya to SUSPEND OPERATIONS OF NICCO BUS SACCO till justice is served on the boys family 

